{"tid":717280,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"為左未來今日遞左信咬老綜扮傻搏公屋","createTime":"2018-06-26T02:06:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-27T03:20:28.000Z","uid":119507,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"9cda2fc6c1560e2aa1b302e95dc3319457dfe9c0","tid":717280,"uid":119507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T02:06:21.000Z","msg":"正苦用盡任何方法 <br />\n1）高樓價政策<br />\n港豬買唔起樓又點會有後代 等我幫同胞封殺你地唯一既安樂窩 睇下你班90後港豬點有子女<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   好彩現今有班人上左車幫手出口術 日日批逗無樓人士 慳水又慳力  呢家有樓既本地港人遲下再清除  <br />\n<br />\n2）人口政策<br />\n日日送150隻炎黃子孫黎 有埋公屋提供 等作生到盤滿缽滿 未來再以量取勝批逗你地地本業主<br />\n<br />\n3）教育政策<br />\n呢家行過幼稚園大部份細蚊仔都係講蝗語，呢個咪陳業主既細路同講廣東話既？一齊欺負佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n正苦膠官不時話大灣區發展好呀，又一帶一路。其實想叫你地契弟快d死上去，咪再留係香港。<br />\n<br />\n我岩岩遞左信 諗住申請綜援 再拎埋白卡上公屋 過下無憂生活  傳宗接代<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1df62006d4bc553ee15dbfe90340b6639e4d0d2f","tid":717280,"uid":82398,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T02:08:18.000Z","msg":"嗯 加油 我繼續住私樓"},{"pid":"f90101116b3282b74d1b1cba6bf35e0b1bfb3f8b","tid":717280,"uid":119507,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"1df62006d4bc553ee15dbfe90340b6639e4d0d2f","tid":717280,"uid":82398,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T02:08:18.000Z","msg":"嗯 加油 我繼續住私樓"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T02:11:28.000Z","msg":"加油 時辰未到姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 今日係屋企無所事事不知幾輕鬆<br />\n<br />\n繼續番工吧"},{"pid":"2707c2cf08b77853580a3b9897e49996c4f04ee3","tid":717280,"uid":82398,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f90101116b3282b74d1b1cba6bf35e0b1bfb3f8b","tid":717280,"uid":119507,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"1